    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A crystalline compound of ammonia and phosphoric acid. It is water soluble and is used most often as a raw material in fertilizers. It is also used as a fire retardant.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
